                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">When is SOE going to do something about swarm kiting?  I was in Nadox with a friend doing the main room where several named are.  Usually this accomodates 3 groups of 6 to each handle 10 spawns.  We went down a side tunnel to do a named and turned around and a bard was swarm kiting all 30 mobs!  This took all of 3 minutes for him and all were dk blue to a 65.  Every other person trying to expl in that area was left with a 30 minute wait or so for respawn or the chice of leaving.  Two groups just left in open disgust.  12 peoples day was ruined by one person's threee minute head trip.
<br />

<br />
SOE purposefully nerfed anything that can help ae groups but still allows Bards to be one-toon ae groups.  I have seen a bard do the entire ME plain with at least 30+ Goranga and several 4 arms trailing.  I have read of one bard at least doing a 125 mob swarm.  If they are going to continue to allow this I want the ae abilities back they took from us.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
