Pacification wasn't nerfed. It was a bug fix. I think a vast majority of people will agree that a 5 minute aggro reducer was *not* the intent of the spell. Yes, it took a long time to fix. But fixed it was. Calling this a nerf is an insult to all the real nerfs that have happened. <img src="images/smiles/icon_wink.gif" alt="icon_wink.gif" border="0" />
